dct_title_s: Peregrinatie der Apostelen ende tleuen Pauli
dct_description_sm: Bar scale statement: Een graet is 20 uren gaens.
Shows topography, waterways, routes of Paul's land and sea voyages.
Pictorial vignettes of episodes in the life of Paul across top and bottom of map, indexed according to text on verso.
Appears in Dutch bible: Den Bybel dat is De Boecken der heyligher Schriftuer uytten oirspronckelijcken Hebreuschen ende Grieckschen ghetrouwelick verduytschet, 1598.
dct_creator_sm: Doetichum, Johan van, the younger, active 1592-1630
dct_publisher_sm: Men vindtse te coop by Krijn Vermeulen de jonghe Cramer ...,
